room_title: Escape room "The Boardwalk" by Escape AC in Atlantic City
review: We had so much fun escaping Boardwalk that we went back the next day for Casino cage. The rooms are very well done! Can't wait to come back and try the harder two rooms!

room_title: Escape room "The Boardwalk" by Escape AC in Atlantic City
review: So much fun! I did this twice already. First the Poker room, then the Boardwalk room. Both of them were awesome and very difficult. We failed to escape the first room, but conquered the second with 13 minutes to spare! Would rate both rooms a 10/10. So much fun, can't wait to go back!
